content.html: Seeing Adele fans party maskless in vegas is why I refuse to pity people who fly across the world for mass events right now, or those who plan them Pure greed drives it whether for profit or pleasure at a time when millions can’t even travel to see loved ones or work
content.value:
Seeing Adele fans party maskless in vegas is why I refuse to pity people who fly across the world for mass events right now, or those who plan them 

Pure greed drives it whether for profit or pleasure at a time when millions can’t even travel to see loved ones or work
